diagnosis.
The IPB has a special unit for rapid detection and diagnosis of diarrheal
diseases (Unit√© des Maladies Infectieuses Opportunistes, Yves Germani, Head
of Unit, germani@intnet.cf).
Samples should be sent to IPB, PO Box 923, BANGUI, Central African Republic.
For viral hemorrhagic fever, please contact J. Morvan (morvan@intnet.cf).
